'From Squeak3.1alpha of 12 February 2001 [latest update: #4039] on 22 May 2001 at 4:13:43 pm'!"Change Set:		collapseFix-bfDate:			22 May 2001Author:			Bert FreudenbergRemoves collapse handle for submorphs to prevent accidentally messing up the morph hierarchy."!!HaloMorph methodsFor: 'handles' stamp: 'bf 5/22/2001 16:05'!addCollapseHandle: handleSpec	"we're hacking here - using mostly dismiss' infrastructure"	| collapseHandle |	(target owner isKindOf: PasteUpMorph)		ifFalse: [^self].	collapseHandle _ self addHandle: handleSpec		on: #mouseDown send: #mouseDownInCollapseHandle:with: to: self.	collapseHandle on: #mouseUp send: #maybeCollapse:with: to: self.	collapseHandle on: #mouseDown send: #setDismissColor:with: to: self.	collapseHandle on: #mouseMove send: #setDismissColor:with: to: self.! !